<article>
<h1>Bankruptcy Cost by Federal District</h1>
<p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.9rem">Last updated: 2026-04-18</p>
<p>Filing fees are set nationally, but attorney fees, case volumes, and dismissal rates vary meaningfully by federal bankruptcy district. These pages combine the 2026 court fee schedule with actual FJC case counts and outcomes, plus market-typical attorney fee ranges for each district's legal market.</p>
<h3>Alabama</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/districts/middle-district-of-alabama.html">Middle District of Alabama</a> - 1,038 cases</li>
<li><a href="/districts/northern-district-of-alabama.html">Northern District of Alabama</a> - 839 cases</li>
</ul>
